---
title: Seared Salmon and Horseradish Sauce with Crisp Apple Salad
description: When a creamy horseradish sauce is involved, you know you’re in for a flavourful and feisty recipe and this dish is no exception! The kickin’ condiment provides a delightful contrast to flaky salmon, crispy roasted potatoes and a bright, apple-studded salad. The best part? It only takes 35 minutes for this stunning dish to land on your table.
